Class ConfigurationProblem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.exception.ConfigurationProblem

  • public class ConfigurationProblem
extends java.lang.Object
    Instances of this class are collected in ConfigurationStatus, which is return value of all checkConfig() methods in the engine. NOTE: ConfigurationException is tighly related class which should be updated respectivelly
